# Setup Overview

The Atlan Python Application SDK requires the following components regardless of operating system:

1. Python 3.11.10
2. Poetry 1.8.5
3. Temporal CLI
4. DAPR CLI 1.14.1
5. Project dependencies

## OS-Specific Setup Guides

Please follow the appropriate guide for your operating system:

- [macOS Setup Guide](mdc:docs/setup/macos.md)
- [Linux Setup Guide](mdc:docs/setup/linux.md)
- [Windows Setup Guide](mdc:docs/setup/windows.md)

